text: Trachylepis principensis is a species of skinks in the family Scincidae. The species is endemic to Príncipe in São Tomé and Príncipe. ==References== Category:Trachylepis Category:Endemic vertebrates of São Tomé and Príncipe Category:Reptiles described in 2016 Category:Taxa named by Luis M.
